{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"idhā"},{"b":"0.36","h":"1.03","c":"السَّمَاءُ","d":"l-samāu","e":"l-samāu"},{"b":"3.2","h":"3.9","c":"انْشَقَّتْ","d":"inshaqqat","e":"inshaqqat"}],"a":{"g":"When the sky has split [open]","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وكان إبراهيم ابن أدهم رحمه الله إذا سمع أحدا يقرأ إذا السماء انشقت اضطربت أوصاله حتى كان يرتعد\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, when Ibrahim ibn Adham, may God have mercy upon him, would hear someone recite \"When the sky is split apart [idha al-sama'u inshaqqat],\" his limbs [awṣāl] would tremble until he would shake.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.2","c":"وَأَذِنَتْ","d":"wa-adhinat","e":"wa-adhinat"},{"b":"0.97","h":"1.68","c":"لِرَبِّهَا","d":"lirabbihā","e":"lirabbihā"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.91","c":"وَحُقَّتْ","d":"waḥuqqat","e":"waḥuqqat"}],"a":{"g":"And has responded to its Lord and was obligated [to do so]"}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.2","c":"وَإِذَا","d":"wa-idhā","e":"wa-idhā"},{"b":"0.6","h":"1.06","c":"الْأَرْضُ","d":"l-arḍu","e":"l-arḍu"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.33","c":"مُدَّتْ","d":"muddat","e":"muddat"}],"a":{"g":"And when the earth has been extended"}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.25","c":"وَأَلْقَتْ","d":"wa-alqat","e":"wa-alqat"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.8","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"mā"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.56","c":"فِيهَا","d":"fīhā","e":"fīhā"},{"b":"2.2","h":"4.24","c":"وَتَخَلَّتْ","d":"watakhallat","e":"watakhallat"}],"a":{"g":"And has cast out that within it and relinquished [it]"}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.3","c":"وَأَذِنَتْ","d":"wa-adhinat","e":"wa-adhinat"},{"b":"0.99","h":"1.79","c":"لِرَبِّهَا","d":"lirabbihā","e":"lirabbihā"},{"b":"2.2","h":"4.14","c":"وَحُقَّتْ","d":"waḥuqqat","e":"waḥuqqat"}],"a":{"g":"And has responded to its Lord and was obligated [to do so] -"}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.2","c":"يَاأَيُّهَا","d":"yāayyuhā","e":"yāayyuhā"},{"b":"2.6","h":"3.35","c":"الْإِنْسَانُ","d":"l-insānu","e":"l-insānu"},{"b":"4.8","h":"5.97","c":"إِنَّكَ","d":"innaka","e":"innaka"},{"b":"6.1","h":"7.72","c":"كَادِحٌ","d":"kādiḥun","e":"kādiḥun"},{"b":"7.3","h":"9.5","c":"إِلَى","d":"ilā","e":"ilā"},{"b":"7.8","h":"10.4","c":"رَبِّكَ","d":"rabbika","e":"rabbika"},{"b":"8.7","h":"12.01","c":"كَدْحًا","d":"kadḥan","e":"kadḥan"},{"b":"10.1","h":"13.82","c":"فَمُلَاقِيهِ","d":"famulāqīhi","e":"famulāqīhi"}],"a":{"g":"O mankind, indeed you are laboring toward your Lord with [great] exertion and will meet it."}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.8","c":"فَأَمَّا","d":"fa-ammā","e":"fa-ammā"},{"b":"1.7","h":"1.26","c":"مَنْ","d":"man","e":"man"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.61","c":"أُوتِيَ","d":"ūtiya","e":"ūtiya"},{"b":"2.9","h":"4.86","c":"كِتَابَهُ","d":"kitābahu","e":"kitābahu"},{"b":"4.2","h":"7.13","c":"بِيَمِينِهِ","d":"biyamīnihi","e":"biyamīnihi"}],"a":{"g":"Then as for he who is given his record in his right hand,"}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.65","c":"فَسَوْفَ","d":"fasawfa","e":"fasawfa"},{"b":"0.77","h":"1.88","c":"يُحَاسَبُ","d":"yuḥāsabu","e":"yuḥāsabu"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.61","c":"حِسَابًا","d":"ḥisāban","e":"ḥisāban"},{"b":"2.6","h":"5.13","c":"يَسِيرًا","d":"yasīran","e":"yasīran"}],"a":{"g":"He will be judged with an easy account","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                من نوقش الحساب عذب قالت قلت يقول الله تعالى فسوف يحاسب حسابا يسيرا قال ذلك العرض\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, he who is subjected to a detailed reckoning [hisab] will be punished. They said, \"I said, 'Allah, the Most High, says: \"He will be brought to an easy reckoning [hisaban yasira].\"'\" He said, \"That is the presentation [al-'ard].\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"9":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"وَيَنْقَلِبُ","d":"wayanqalibu","e":"wayanqalibu"},{"b":"1.9","h":"3.02","c":"إِلَى","d":"ilā","e":"ilā"},{"b":"3.7","h":"5.14","c":"أَهْلِهِ","d":"ahlihi","e":"ahlihi"},{"b":"4.8","h":"6.95","c":"مَسْرُورًا","d":"masrūran","e":"masrūran"}],"a":{"g":"And return to his people in happiness."}},"10":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.43","c":"وَأَمَّا","d":"wa-ammā","e":"wa-ammā"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.38","c":"مَنْ","d":"man","e":"man"},{"b":"2.2","h":"3.16","c":"أُوتِيَ","d":"ūtiya","e":"ūtiya"},{"b":"3.0","h":"4.43","c":"كِتَابَهُ","d":"kitābahu","e":"kitābahu"},{"b":"4.3","h":"6.86","c":"وَرَاءَ","d":"warāa","e":"warāa"},{"b":"6.7","h":"9.12","c":"ظَهْرِهِ","d":"ẓahrihi","e":"ẓahrihi"}],"a":{"g":"But as for he who is given his record behind his back,"}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.4","c":"فَسَوْفَ","d":"fasawfa","e":"fasawfa"},{"b":"0.72","h":"1.63","c":"يَدْعُوا","d":"yadʿū","e":"yadʿū"},{"b":"1.5","h":"3.06","c":"ثُبُورًا","d":"thubūran","e":"thubūran"}],"a":{"g":"He will cry out for destruction"}},"12":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","h":"0.45","c":"وَيَصْلَى","d":"wayaṣlā","e":"wayaṣlā"},{"b":"0.94","h":"2.21","c":"سَعِيرًا","d":"saʿīran","e":"saʿīran"}],"a":{"g":"And [enter to] burn in a Blaze."}},"13":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.5","c":"إِنَّهُ","d":"innahu","e":"innahu"},{"b":"1.6","h":"2.49","c":"كَانَ","d":"kāna","e":"kāna"},{"b":"2.3","h":"3.7","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"fī"},{"b":"3.9","h":"5.51","c":"أَهْلِهِ","d":"ahlihi","e":"ahlihi"},{"b":"5.0","h":"7.27","c":"مَسْرُورًا","d":"masrūran","e":"masrūran"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, he had [once] been among his people in happiness;"}},"14":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.3","c":"إِنَّهُ","d":"innahu","e":"innahu"},{"b":"1.5","h":"2.28","c":"ظَنَّ","d":"ẓanna","e":"ẓanna"},{"b":"3.1","h":"3.74","c":"أَنْ","d":"an","e":"an"},{"b":"3.3","h":"4.06","c":"لَنْ","d":"lan","e":"lan"},{"b":"4.8","h":"5.79","c":"يَحُورَ","d":"yaḥūra","e":"yaḥūra"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, he had thought he would never return [to Allah]."}},"15":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1","c":"بَلَى","d":"balā","e":"balā"},{"b":"1.2","h":"3.44","c":"إِنَّ","d":"inna","e":"inna"},{"b":"2.4","h":"4.69","c":"رَبَّهُ","d":"rabbahu","e":"rabbahu"},{"b":"3.4","h":"6.46","c":"كَانَ","d":"kāna","e":"kāna"},{"b":"4.0","h":"7.62","c":"بِهِ","d":"bihi","e":"bihi"},{"b":"4.7","h":"8.76","c":"بَصِيرًا","d":"baṣīran","e":"baṣīran"}],"a":{"g":"But yes! Indeed, his Lord was ever of him, Seeing."}},"16":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.4","c":"فَلَا","d":"falā","e":"falā"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.08","c":"أُقْسِمُ","d":"uq'simu","e":"uq'simu"},{"b":"2.8","h":"3.46","c":"بِالشَّفَقِ","d":"bil-shafaqi","e":"bil-shafaqi"}],"a":{"g":"So I swear by the twilight glow"}},"17":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.5","c":"وَاللَّيْلِ","d":"wa-al-layli","e":"wa-al-layli"},{"b":"1.0","h":"2.1","c":"وَمَا","d":"wamā","e":"wamā"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.22","c":"وَسَقَ","d":"wasaqa","e":"wasaqa"}],"a":{"g":"And [by] the night and what it envelops"}},"18":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.2","c":"وَالْقَمَرِ","d":"wal-qamari","e":"wal-qamari"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.79","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"idhā"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.36","c":"اتَّسَقَ","d":"ittasaqa","e":"ittasaqa"}],"a":{"g":"And [by] the moon when it becomes full"}},"19":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","h":"0.45","c":"لَتَرْكَبُنَّ","d":"latarkabunna","e":"latarkabunna"},{"b":"2.2","h":"2.88","c":"طَبَقًا","d":"ṭabaqan","e":"ṭabaqan"},{"b":"3.1","h